Another odd thing: with prophetic care I took down in my diary all mystops, all my motels (Mes Moteaux as Verlaine might have said!), theLakeviews, the Valley Views, the Mountain Views, the Plumed Serpent Court inNew Mexico, the Lolita Lodge in Texas, Lone Poplars, that if recruited mighthave patrolled a whole river, and enough sunsets to keep all the bats of theworld--and one dying genius--happy. LATH, LATH, Look At